bug.author: mehrdadh
bug.summary: RangeError Maximum call stack size exceeded with MobileBert model
bug.description:
I tried to visualize the saved models from mobilebert and ran into this error. Here is a link to .pb files: <denchmark-link:https://storage.googleapis.com/cloud-tpu-checkpoints/mobilebert/mobilebert_squad_savedmodels.tar.gz>https://storage.googleapis.com/cloud-tpu-checkpoints/mobilebert/mobilebert_squad_savedmodels.tar.gz</denchmark-link>
However I tried with the tflite version from this link and it worked: <denchmark-link:https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/tflite/bert_qa/mobilebert_float_20191023.tflite>https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/tflite/bert_qa/mobilebert_float_20191023.tflite</denchmark-link>
Please let me know if you need more information to reproduce the error. Thanks
